  "text": "Meta-Opt Net [CITATION_1] : The class representation function is a hyperplane that is learned while training an SVM on the task. c k = φ w ({z j | y j = k}) s.t. c k z j > 0. Membership is then calculated based on the distance to each hyperplane.",
